OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry but rather cloudy
OL,6,Facross southern parts today.
OL,7,FElsewhere, a band of rain,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy, will gradually
OL,9,Fmove southeastwards, with scattered
OL,10,Fblustery showers following behind.
OL,11,FWidely windy, with gales in the north
OL,12,Fwhere it will also turn colder later.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FThe band of rain continuing
OL,15,Fto move southeastwards, clearing East
OL,16,FAnglia during the early hours.
OL,17,FScattered blustery showers following,
OL,18,Fwith these turning wintry in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
