OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FSunny spells and blustery
OL,6,Fwintry showers. The showers most
OL,7,Ffrequent across the north and
OL,8,Fnorthwest where they will be heavy
OL,9,Fwith hail and thunder. Feeling cold
OL,10,Fwith brisk winds.
